Subject: Secunia Research: TaskFreak "tznMessage"
	Cross-Site Scripting Vulnerability

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 29/06/2010

     - TaskFreak "tznMessage" Cross-Site Scripting Vulnerability -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

